
INSTRUCTIONS
============

The app is in maintenance mode as long as a file named "maintenance_mode_on" is
present. Otherwise the app is not in maintenance mode.

	ENABLING MAINTENANCE MODE
	-------------------------
	
	To enable maintenance mode, create a file named "maintenance_mode_on". You
	could also just rename this file here.
	
	
	DISABLING MAINTENANCE MODE
	--------------------------
	
	To disable maintenance mode, delete the file named "maintenance_mode_on".
	You could also just rename it from "maintenance_mode_on" to something else,
	i.e. to "maintenance_mode_off".